  "title": "Question on the page \"connectGeoSearch\"",
  "body": "Hi! I have a documentation issue on InstantSearch.js. I could not find what I was looking for on the page \"[connectGeoSearch](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors/connectGeoSearch.html)\".\r\n\r\nCould you help me understand how to use the `refine` and `setMapMoveSinceLastRefine` functions to enable map-move refinement with a Leaflet implementation? \r\n\r\nThe example doesn't deal with this, and I wasn't able to understand how to use it from the test fixture or source code. \r\n\r\nThank you!\r\nChris\r\n",
